79633>>>>>// *WvA: 13-01-1999 Created
79633>>>>>// The Class cSelectFile_Dialog is created to support the function Select_File
79633>>>>>// This function opens the Windows standard file open dialog and returns the selected
79633>>>>>// file_name.
79633>>>>>Class cvSelectFile_Dialog Is An OpenDialog
79634>>>>>
79634>>>>>  Procedure Construct_Object Integer iImage_Id
79636>>>>>    Forward Send Construct_Object iImage_Id
79638>>>>>    Set HideReadOnly_State To True
79639>>>>>  End_Procedure // Construct_Object
79640>>>>>
79640>>>>>  Function SelectedFileName Returns String
79642>>>>>    String sFileName
79642>>>>>    Move "" To sFileName
79643>>>>>    If (Show_Dialog(Self)) Begin
79645>>>>>      Move (RTrim(File_Name(Self))) To sFileName
79646>>>>>    End
79646>>>>>>
79646>>>>>    Function_Return sFileName
79647>>>>>  End_Function // SelectedFileName
79648>>>>>End_Class // cvSelectFile_Dialog
79649>>>>>
79649>>>>>
79649>>>>>// *WvA: 13-01-1999 Created
79649>>>>>// This function opens the Windows standard file open dialog and returns the selected
79649>>>>>// file_name. Returns '' if the user didn't make a selection.
79649>>>>>// **WvA: 17-10-2003 Cleaned up and added code to destroy the dynamically created
79649>>>>>//                   file-open dialog
79649>>>>>Function vSelect_File Global String sSupportedFileTypes String sCaptionText String sInitialFolder Returns String
79651>>>>>  String sSelectedFile
79651>>>>>  Integer hoOpenFileDialog
79651>>>>>  
79651>>>>>  Object oOpenFileDialog Is A cvSelectFile_Dialog 
79653>>>>>
79653>>>>>    Set Dialog_Caption    To sCaptionText
79654>>>>>    Set Filter_String     To sSupportedFileTypes
79655>>>>>    Set Initial_Folder    To sInitialFolder
79656>>>>>    
79656>>>>>    Move Self       To hoOpenFileDialog
79657>>>>>  End_Object // oOpenFileDialog         
79658>>>>>  
79658>>>>>  Get SelectedFileName Of hoOpenFileDialog To sSelectedFile
79659>>>>>  Send Destroy_Object To hoOpenFileDialog
79660>>>>>  Function_Return sSelectedFile
79661>>>>>End_Function // vSelect_File   
79662>>>>>
