80152>>>Function vConvertFileDateTime Global Dword dwLowDateTime Dword dwHighDateTime Returns String
80154>>>  String  sftTime sSystemTime sFormattedTime sFormattedDate
80154>>>  Pointer lpsftTime lpsSystemTime lpsFormattedTime lpsFormattedDate
80154>>>  Integer iSuccess iLenCcTime iDataLength iLenCcDate
80154>>>
80154>>>  ZeroType vFileTime  To sftTime
80155>>>  Put dwLowDateTime  To sftTime At vFileTime.dwLowDateTime
80156>>>  Put dwHighDateTime To sftTime At vFileTime.dwHighDateTime
80157>>>  GetAddress Of sftTime To lpsftTime
80158>>>
80158>>>  ZeroType vSystemTime To sSystemTime
80159>>>  GetAddress Of sSystemTime To lpsSystemTime
80160>>>
80160>>>  Moveint (vWin32_FileTimeToSystemTime (lpsftTime, lpsSystemTime)) To iSuccess
80161>>>>
80161>>>  If iSuccess Eq DfTrue Begin
80163>>>    ZeroString 255 To sFormattedTime
80164>>>    GetAddress Of sFormattedTime To lpsFormattedTime
80165>>>    Length sFormattedTime To iLenCcTime
80166>>>>
80166>>>    Moveint (vWin32_GetTimeFormat (LOCALE_USER_DEFAULT, 0, lpsSystemTime, 0, ;                             lpsFormattedTime, iLenCcTime)) To iDataLength
80167>>>>
