82114>>>>>//****************************************************************************
82114>>>>>// $Module type: Class
82114>>>>>// $Module name: cSQLConnectionHandler.pkg
82114>>>>>// $Author     : Nils G. Svedmyr, RDC Tools International, <mailto:support@rdctools.com>
82114>>>>>// Web-site    : http://www.rdctools.com
82114>>>>>// Created     : 2015-08-11 @ 16:02 (Military date format: YY-MM-DD)
82114>>>>>//
82114>>>>>// Description : A handler class for using CLI connection ID's to login to a database server.
82114>>>>>//
82114>>>>>// $Rev History:
82114>>>>>//    2015-08-11  Module header created
82114>>>>>//    2016-09-26  Changed name of the objecthandle from ghoCreateConnectionID to ghoSQLConnectionHandler.
82114>>>>>//                Added a new structure for passing connection data back & forth.
82114>>>>>//                Added better error handling.
82114>>>>>//                Added a decompose message for the connection string.
82114>>>>>//    2017-01-09  Added support for Mertech drivers
82114>>>>>//                Big overhaul to comply better with "Managed Connections" (DF 19)
82114>>>>>//                These changes make the class compatible with DFConnId.ini (can read/write DAW connection ini-files)
82114>>>>>//    2017-02-12  Reworked the whole connection property interface.
82114>>>>>//                Now there is one struct property that is the at cencter of a connection.
82114>>>>>//****************************************************************************
