82162>>>>>>>>>    Function DbLogin String sConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns Boolean
82164>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bLoginSuccessful
82164>>>>>>>>>        String sDriverID 
82164>>>>>>>>>        
82164>>>>>>>>>        Move False to Err
82165>>>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID
82166>>>>>>>>>        If (not(Uppercase(sServer) contains "DSN")) Begin
82168>>>>>>>>>            Move ("DSN=" + sServer) to sServer
82169>>>>>>>>>        End
82169>>>>>>>>>>
82169>>>>>>>>>        Login sServer sUserId sPassword sDriverID
82171>>>>>>>>>        
82171>>>>>>>>>        Move (not(Err)) to bLoginSuccessful
82172>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return bLoginSuccessful
82173>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
82174>>>>>>>>>End_Class
