82246>>>>>>>>>Class cDbUpdateDatabaseDriver is a cObject
82247>>>>>>>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
82249>>>>>>>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
82251>>>>>>>>>        Property String psDriverID DATAFLEX_ID
82252>>>>>>>>>        Property Handle phoDriverSpecificObject
82253>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
82254>>>>>>>>>    
82254>>>>>>>>>    Function CreateDriver Returns Handle
82256>>>>>>>>>        String sDriverID
82256>>>>>>>>>        Handle hoDriver hcDriverClass
82256>>>>>>>>>        
82256>>>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID
82257>>>>>>>>>        Case Begin
82257>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MSSQLDRV_ID)
82259>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateMSSQLDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82260>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82261>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = ODBC_DRV_ID)
82264>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateODBCDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82265>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82266>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = DB2_DRV_ID)
82269>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateDB2Driver)) to hcDriverClass
82270>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82271>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = SQLFLEX)
82274>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateSQLFLEXDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82275>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82276>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = ORAFLEX)
82279>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateORAFLEXDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82280>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82281>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MDSPgSQL)
82284>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateMDSPgSQLDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82285>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82286>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MDSMySQL)
82289>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateMDSMySQLDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82290>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82291>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = DATAFLEX_ID)
82294>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateDataFlexDriver)) to hcDriverClass
82295>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
82296>>>>>>>>>            Case Else
82296>>>>>>>>>                Function_Return 0
82297>>>>>>>>>        Case End
82297>>>>>>>>>        
82297>>>>>>>>>        Get Create hcDriverClass to hoDriver
82298>>>>>>>>>        Set psDriverID of hoDriver to sDriverID
82299>>>>>>>>>        Set phoDriverSpecificObject to hoDriver
82300>>>>>>>>>        
82300>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return hoDriver
82301>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
82302>>>>>>>>>    
82302>>>>>>>>>    Procedure DestroyDriver
82304>>>>>>>>>        If (phoDriverSpecificObject(Self)) Begin
82306>>>>>>>>>            Send Destroy of (phoDriverSpecificObject(Self))
82307>>>>>>>>>        End
82307>>>>>>>>>>
82307>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
82308>>>>>>>>>    
82308>>>>>>>>>    Function ConstructConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns String
82310>>>>>>>>>        String sConnect
82310>>>>>>>>>        Handle hoDriver
82310>>>>>>>>>        
82310>>>>>>>>>        Get CreateDriver to hoDriver
82311>>>>>>>>>        Get ConstructConnectionString of hoDriver sServer sDatabase bTrusted sUserID sPassword to sConnect
82312>>>>>>>>>        Send DestroyDriver
82313>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return sConnect
82314>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
82315>>>>>>>>>    
82315>>>>>>>>>    Function DbLogin String sConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns Boolean
82317>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bLoginSuccessful
82317>>>>>>>>>        Handle hoDriver
82317>>>>>>>>>        
82317>>>>>>>>>        Get CreateDriver to hoDriver
82318>>>>>>>>>        Get DbLogin of hoDriver sConnectionString sServer sDatabase bTrusted sUserID sPassword to bLoginSuccessful
82319>>>>>>>>>        Send DestroyDriver
82320>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return bLoginSuccessful
82321>>>>>>>>>    End_Function 
82322>>>>>>>>>    
82322>>>>>>>>>End_Class
