82359>>>>>>>
82359>>>>>>>    // *** Generalized messages to Get & Set values of the ini file.
82359>>>>>>>    // Sets a value in the program's ini file (write)
82359>>>>>>>    // Pass a section name, the value name parameter and the value itself to be written.
82359>>>>>>>    Procedure Set IniFileValue String sSection String sValueName String sValue
82361>>>>>>>        String sIniFile sPath
82361>>>>>>>
82361>>>>>>>        Get psIniFilePath to sPath   
82362>>>>>>>        Get psIniFileName to sIniFile
82363>>>>>>>        Move (sPath + sIniFile) to sIniFile
82364>>>>>>>        Set psFileName to sIniFile
82365>>>>>>>        Send WriteString sSection sValueName sValue
82366>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
82367>>>>>>>
82367>>>>>>>    // Get a value from program's ini-file (read)
82367>>>>>>>    // Pass a section name and the name of the value parameter & a default value.
82367>>>>>>>    // Returns the value
82367>>>>>>>    Function IniFileValue String sSection String sValueName String sDefaultValue Returns String
82369>>>>>>>        String sValue sIniFile sPath
82369>>>>>>>
82369>>>>>>>        Get psIniFilePath to sPath
82370>>>>>>>        Get psIniFileName to sIniFile
82371>>>>>>>        Move (sPath + sIniFile) to sIniFile
82372>>>>>>>        Set psFileName to sIniFile
82373>>>>>>>        Get ReadString sSection sValueName sDefaultValue to sValue
82374>>>>>>>
82374>>>>>>>        Function_Return sValue
82375>>>>>>>    End_Function                     
