82894>>>>>        Get IsDAWSQLDriver sDriverID to bOK
82895>>>>>
82895>>>>>        If (bOK = False) Begin
82897>>>>>            Get IsMertechDriver sDriverID to bOK
82898>>>>>        End                                     
82898>>>>>>
82898>>>>>
82898>>>>>        Function_Return bOK
82899>>>>>    End_Function
82900>>>>>            
