83018>>>>>            Get ConstructConnectionString SQLConnection.sDriverID SQLConnection.sServer SQLConnection.sDatabase SQLConnection.bTrusted SQLConnection.sUserID SQLConnection.sPassword to SQLConnection.sConnectionString
83019>>>>>        End
83019>>>>>>
83019>>>>>    End_Procedure
