86316>>>            Get SQLConnect of hoSQLHandler SQLConnection.sDriverID SQLConnection.sServer SQLConnection.sUserID SQLConnection.sPassword to hoSQLConnect
86317>>>            If (hoSQLConnect <> 0) Begin   
