87412>>>        Open hTable Mode DF_EXCLUSIVE
87414>>>        Get_Attribute DF_FIELD_NAME of hTable iOld to sColumn
87417>>>        Get_Attribute DF_FIELD_TYPE of hTable iOld to iType
87420>>>    
