87427>>>            Get_Attribute DF_FIELD_PRECISION of hTable iOld to iPrecision
87430>>>        End
87430>>>>
87430>>>        Move False to Err
87431>>>    
87431>>>        Structure_Start hTable  
87432>>>            Delete_Field hTable iOld
87433>>>            Create_Field hTable At iNew
87434>>>            Set_Attribute DF_FIELD_NAME of hTable iNew to sColumn
87437>>>            Set_Attribute DF_FIELD_TYPE of hTable iNew to iType
87440>>>    
