87477>>>    // Renames a field for the passed table number & old field name & new field name
87477>>>    // Returns True if no errors occured.
87477>>>    // Sample usage:
87477>>>    //   Get ColumnRename Quote.File_Number "ID#" "ID" to bOK
87477>>>    Function ApiColumnRename Integer hTable String sOldFieldName String sNewFieldName Returns Boolean
87479>>>        Integer iField
87479>>>        Boolean bOK
