87484>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id DFERR_DUPLICATE_FIELDNAME
87485>>>        Structure_Start hTable
87486>>>            Field_Map hTable sOldFieldName to iField
87488>>>            If (iField > 0) Begin
87490>>>                Set_Attribute DF_FIELD_NAME of hTable iField to sNewFieldName
87493>>>            End
