89877>>>    // Similar to _SqlCheckCurrentDriver but generates no error and it doesn't 
89877>>>    // attempt to load the driver.
89877>>>    // Returns true if the passed driver is SQL based.        
89877>>>    Function IsSQLDriver String sDriverID Returns Boolean
89879>>>        Boolean bOK                         
89879>>>        Integer iDriver
89879>>>        
89879>>>        Get IsDAWSQLDriver sDriverID to bOK
89880>>>
