90073>>>    // The normal connection string looks something like this;
90073>>>    // SERVER=.\SQLEXPRESS; DATABASE=OrderEntry; TRUSTED_CONNECTION=Yes; ,0
90073>>>    // ...and the full connection string looks like this;
90073>>>    // DFConnectionId OrderEntry, SERVER=.\SQLEXPRESS; DATABASE=OrderEntry; TRUSTED_CONNECTION=Yes; ,0
90073>>>    Function psFullConnectionString Returns String
90075>>>        String sConnectionID sConnectionString
90075>>>        If (ghoSQLConnectionHandler = 0) Begin
