90079>>>        End                                                                   
90079>>>>
90079>>>        Get psConnectionID     of ghoSQLConnectionHandler to sConnectionID                       
90080>>>        Move (Trim(sConnectionID)) to sConnectionID
90081>>>        Get psConnectionString of ghoSQLConnectionHandler to sConnectionString
90082>>>        Function_Return (CS_SQLConnectionIDText * sConnectionID + "," * String(sConnectionString))
90083>>>    End_Function
