91374>>>>>>>>>>>// 10/15/97 JJT - changed define_symbol to define
91374>>>>>>>>>>>// 6/27/97  JJT - Modified low level help calls to work better in 95 help.
91374>>>>>>>>>>>// 07/23/96 JJT - New Class names
91374>>>>>>>>>>>// 01/27/96 JJT - Changed to from DAF to DF
91374>>>>>>>>>>>// 02/14/95 JJT - Added DFGSINI for 3.01/3.05 dual support of .ini name
91374>>>>>>>>>>>//                and section name.
