91496>>>>>>>>>>>    procedure View_Error_Help Integer Obj
91498>>>>>>>>>>>        String Context
91498>>>>>>>>>>>        If Obj gt 0 ;           Get Help_Context of obj HELP_CONTEXT_ERROR to Context
91501>>>>>>>>>>>        if (left(context,1)) in '0123456789' ;           Get System_Help_Error_id Context to Context
91504>>>>>>>>>>>        Send Exec_Context_Help Context
91505>>>>>>>>>>>    end_procedure
