91614>>>>>    // Augmented class message to adjust certain text strings that are wrong...
91614>>>>>
91614>>>>>    Procedure AppendTextLn String sText
91616>>>>>        String sWorkspaceWSFile
91616>>>>>
91616>>>>>        // Only works for English:
91616>>>>>        If (ghoApplication > 0) Begin
91618>>>>>            If (sText contains "Workspace Name") Begin
91620>>>>>                Move "Workspace Config Filename:" to sText
91621>>>>>                Get psWorkspaceWSFile of (phoWorkspace(ghoApplication)) to sWorkspaceWSFile
91622>>>>>                Move (sText * sWorkspaceWSFile) to sText
91623>>>>>            End
91623>>>>>>
91623>>>>>        End
91623>>>>>>
91623>>>>>        Send AppendText sText
91624>>>>>        Send AppendText (character(10))
91625>>>>>    End_Procedure
