91999>>>>>//****************************************************************************
91999>>>>>// $Module type: OBJECT
91999>>>>>// $Module name: Sysinfo_Dialog
91999>>>>>// $Author     : VOO
91999>>>>>// Created     : 24-09-96 @ 18:47
91999>>>>>//
91999>>>>>// Description
91999>>>>>//    This object shows the systeminformation on the screen
91999>>>>>//
91999>>>>>// $Rev History
91999>>>>>//    24-09-96  Module header created
91999>>>>>//****************************************************************************
91999>>>>>Class SysInfoDialog is a ModalPanel
92000>>>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
92002>>>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
92004>>>>>
92004>>>>>        Set Label to C_$SystemInformation
92005>>>>>        Set Size to 140 267
92006>>>>>        Set Locate_Mode to CENTER_ON_PARENT
92007>>>>>        Set Border_Style to Border_Thick
92008>>>>>        Set Sysmenu_Icon to False
92009>>>>>
92009>>>>>        // "+1" will make the panel to paint correctly.
92009>>>>>        Set piMinSize to (Hi(Size(Self))) (Low(Size(Self)) +1)
92010>>>>>
92010>>>>>        // 2014-09-14 NGS
92010>>>>>        // Added a container object around the cTexteditor
92010>>>>>        // object to get a border around the text.
92010>>>>>        Object oSysinfoDisplayContainer is a Container3d
92012>>>>>            Set Location to 2 4
92013>>>>>            Set Size to 110 255
92014>>>>>            Set Border_Style to Border_ClientEdge
92015>>>>>            Set Color to clWhite
92016>>>>>            Set peAnchors to anAll
92017>>>>>
92017>>>>>            Object oSysinfoDisplay is a SysInfoDisplay
92019>>>>>            End_Object
92020>>>>>
92020>>>>>        End_Object
92021>>>>>
92021>>>>>        Object oCloseButton is a Button
92023>>>>>            Set Label to C_$Close
92024>>>>>            Set Location to 120 210
92025>>>>>            Set Message item 0 to msg_Close_Panel
92026>>>>>            Set Default_State To True
92027>>>>>            // In case someone likes to make the AboutDialog's Border_Style to thick,
92027>>>>>            // and changes its peAnchors, we might as well prepare this object
92027>>>>>            // for that situation.
92027>>>>>            Set peAnchors to anBottomRight
92028>>>>>        End_Object
92029>>>>>
92029>>>>>        Object oCopyButton is a cCopyEditorContentButton
92031>>>>>            On_Item C_$Copy Send CopyToWindowsClipboard
92032>>>>>            Set Size to 14 50
92033>>>>>            Set Location to 120 158
92034>>>>>            // In case someone wants to set the AboutDialog's Border_Style to thick,
92034>>>>>            // we might as well prepare the object for it.
92034>>>>>            Set peAnchors to anBottomRight
92035>>>>>            Set phoEditorHandle to (oSysinfoDisplay(Self))
92036>>>>>        End_Object
92037>>>>>
92037>>>>>        On_Key kCancel Send Close_Panel
92038>>>>>    End_Procedure
92039>>>>>
