92044>>>>>End_Class
92045>>>>>
92045>>>>>Class cAboutEdit is an cRichEdit
92046>>>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
92048>>>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
92050>>>>>
92050>>>>>        Set Size to 57 153
92051>>>>>        Set Location to 8 60
92052>>>>>
92052>>>>>        Set Read_Only_State to True
92053>>>>>        Set Skip_State to True
92054>>>>>        // Font size is calculated in "Twips", which are 1/1440 of an inch,
92054>>>>>        // or 1/20 of a printer's point.
92054>>>>>//        Set piFontSize    to (9 * 20)
92054>>>>>        Set piRightMargin to (0.1 * 1440)
92055>>>>>        Set Border_Style  to Border_None
92056>>>>>    End_Procedure
92057>>>>>
92057>>>>>    // Adds a line of text to the edit object
92057>>>>>    Procedure Add_Line String sVal
92059>>>>>        String sText
92059>>>>>        Address aAddress
92059>>>>>        Get paValue to aAddress
92060>>>>>        Move aAddress to sText
92061>>>>>        Move (sText + String(sVal)) to sVal
92062>>>>>        GetAddress of sVal to aAddress
92063>>>>>        Set paValue to aAddress
92064>>>>>    End_Procedure
92065>>>>>
92065>>>>>    // Compared to Add_Line above, this adds an extra empty line after the passed value.
92065>>>>>    // Note that we use the paValue interface,
92065>>>>>    // because the object isn't paged yet when we add the
92065>>>>>    // values and the COM edit object needs to be paged
92065>>>>>    // for the "Set Value" interface to be used.
92065>>>>>    Procedure Add_LineLn String sVal
92067>>>>>        String sText
92067>>>>>        Address aAddress
92067>>>>>        Get paValue to aAddress
92068>>>>>        Move aAddress to sText
92069>>>>>        Move (sText + String(sVal) + Character(10) + Character(13)) to sVal
92070>>>>>        GetAddress of sVal to aAddress
92071>>>>>        Set paValue to aAddress
92072>>>>>    End_Procedure
92073>>>>>
92073>>>>>    Procedure OnLinkClicked Integer iPositionStart Integer iPositionEnd
92075>>>>>        String sLinkText
92075>>>>>        Get TextRange iPositionStart iPositionEnd to sLinkText
92076>>>>>        Send Show_HomePage sLinkText
92077>>>>>    End_Procedure
92078>>>>>
92078>>>>>End_Class
92079>>>>>
92079>>>>>// Purpose:
92079>>>>>//
92079>>>>>// Ken Ross 12/17/96 5:16PM
92079>>>>>//
92079>>>>>Class AboutDialog is a ModalPanel
92080>>>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
92082>>>>>
92082>>>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
92084>>>>>
92084>>>>>        Set Label to C_$About
92085>>>>>        Set Size to 96 230
